    "name": "E2E Referral Commission Workflow",
    "description": "Complete end-to-end workflow: User Registration → Referral → Commission → Wallet Rewards\n\nThis collection demonstrates how all pillars work together:\n1. Setup referral program and enroll User A (referrer)\n2. User B registers using User A's referral\n3. User B completes qualifying action\n4. System records commission for User A\n5. System deposits reward coins into User A's wallet",
